flowchart TD
    A[Team Lead creates task] --> B[Task assigned to specialist]
    B --> C[Specialist accepts and starts]
    C --> D{Specialist working}
    D -->|Progress| E[TaskUpdate: intermediate state]
    E --> D
    D -->|Completed| F[TaskUpdate: final result]
    F --> G[Team Lead receives update]
    G --> H{More tasks needed?}
    H -->|Yes| A
    H -->|No| I[Aggregated results]
